ty high  rising dividend equity the diversifier fixed income custom tailored solutions manager of managers program media bswmg in the news financial markets commentary contact us investment philosophy asset allocation  diversification individuals foundations and family offices can derive benefit from barrington’s investment road map the investment roadmap allows us to customtailor an investment program just for you asset allocation and diversification feature prominently in a tailored strategy to be effective asset allocation must be dynamic asset allocation we believe that asset allocation is more important to overall performance and volatility reduction than almost any other decision each investor’s allocation is different depending on his or her combination of goals time horizon and risk tolerance your own allocation might utilize some combination of equity fixed income alternative strategies cash equivalents and real estaterelated investments diversification diversification means achieving a blend of individual investments within asset classes to accomplish a specific riskreward goal to be effective diversification should dynamically reflect the future probabilities not look backward at the past these asset allocation wheels are examples of allocations that may be appropriate for some investors at a point in time an investor’s particular goals circumstances and risk tolerance will dictate the appropriate allocation for that investor the allocation wheels are presented here only to reflect how diversification may look under a given set of circumstances all investments have some risk some of these strategies have more risk than traditional investments diversified allocation example december   click for larger view this grid of returns for nine asset classes features the best performing asset classes at the top and the worst performing asset classes at the bottom of each year clearly diversification reflective of the economic environment can moderate volatility click chart to enlarge   home    about us    investment philosophy    investment strategies    media    contact us    disclaimer    site map what makes us unique about us what makes us unique our team investment philosophy asset allocation  diversification investment strategies all cap value equity growth and value blend equity high  rising dividend equity the diversifier fixed income custom tailored solutions manager of managers program media bswmg in the news financial markets commentary contact us what makes us unique we are a boutique investment management firm focused exclusively on helping our clients to reach their financial goals we are known for our dedicated client service we are independent and do not have affiliated investment banking or brokerage arms which could conflict with our focus on our clients best interests our incisive written analysis of macroeconomic and financial issues provides the framework for asset allocation and informs sector and specific investment selections clients know where we stand on economic and investment issues our singular focus allows us to be decisive and nimble attributes of particular value in tumultuous times we work hard to earn our clients trust through a dedicated focus on their needs and integrity in our decision making we offer multiple investment strategies which can be combined to meet each client’s goals our structure provides additional peace of mind for clients bswmg manages client assets we do not hold them your investments are held at a custodian of your choosing in separate accounts held in the legal title of those accounts you receive separate statements of holdings and confirmations of transactions directly from this separate custodian this data flows into our portfolio management system which is reconciled daily by the portfolio management software firm with the data available at your custodian reconciliations are performed on a bestefforts basis the securities underlying your account’s performance are independently visible on the custodial statements so that anyone viewing them could ascertain their likelihood of generating the stated performance we do not receive commissions on the transactions made in your accounts we are solely compensated via fees based upon your account’s valuation unlike some managers that charge fees and commissions we forego the extra commission revenue to obviate any actual as well as potential conflicts of interest in our investments for you we do not have the ability to move money outside of your accounts in your name with the exception of management fees we do this for your protection and for ours integrity and transparency provide a true value proposition for the client   home    about us    investment philosophy    investment strategies    media    contact us    disclaimer    site map fixed income about us what makes us unique our team investment philosophy asset allocation  diversification investment strategies all cap value equity growth and value blend equity high  rising dividend equity the diversifier fixed income custom tailored solutions manager of managers program media bswmg in the news financial markets commentary contact us fixed income barrington strategic wealth management group manages both taxable and taxexempt fixed income portfolios we tailor our portfolios based upon your income needs risk tolerance and long term goals municipals treasuries corporates agencies and high yield are among the fixed income vehicles utilized to create a diversified fixed income ladder typically we maintain a  year duration but will extend or reduce based upon the market environment risk ratings and the current economic climate are all reviewed continually to maximize selection and ensure original fixed income guidelines and parameters are adhered to   home    about us    investment philosophy    investment strategies    media    contact us    disclaimer    site map barrington strategic wealth management group llc  wealthminder barrington st