itative analysi barrington strategic wealth management group llc is an employee owned investment manager the firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals it also caters to banking or thrift institutions pension and profit sharing plans charitable organizations corporations and other businesses the firm manages separate clientfocused equity fixed income and balanced portfolios it invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe the firm primarily invests in growth and value stocks across all market capitalization ranging from  million to over  billion having maturity from  to  years it uses a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis with topdown and bottomup stock picking approach the firm also invests in instruments like exchange traded funds and employs short and longshort strategies to create its portfolio for its fixed income portion of the portfolio it invests in securities issued by municipals treasuries corporate and agencies mortgage backed securities and global and high yield bonds the firm invests in dividend stocks it typically invests in diversified sectors barrington strategic wealth management group llc was founded in may  and is based in chicago illinois detailed description  north franklin streetsuite chicago il united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwbswmgcom key executives for barrington strategic wealth management group llc ms diana jill joseph jd managing director managing member and chief investment officer mrs ellen penrod abell managing director ms lauren michelle genuardi managing director and portfolio manager ms emily stuart rodgers managing director of operations ms katrine ellen vange keller cpa director and chief compliance officer compensation as of fiscal year  similar private companies by industry company name region visory llc united states  road partners llc united states t partners llc united states jumpcom inc united states  ontario inc united states recent private companies t